          "en": "When the people pledged allegiance to Abu Bakr, Fatimah the daughter of Muhammad, may Allah bless him and his family, came out and stood at her door and said: 'Never have I witnessed a day like this. They have indeed set the worst precedent. They left their Prophet, may Allah bless him and his family, as a corpse in our midst and monopolized the matter without us.'",
